00:17:51,267 --> 00:17:53,067
Toasted bread.
Fresh sausage.

270
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:54,500
Fresh pork sausage.

271
00:17:54,533 --> 00:17:57,133
And a cheese and a spicy sauce.

272
00:17:57,167 --> 00:17:58,833
And spicy sauce.

