00:18:20,567 --> 00:18:21,733
Mmm. This is delicious.

282
00:18:21,767 --> 00:18:23,400
This is very healthy too.

283
00:18:23,433 --> 00:18:25,400
Yeah, it's a light dinner.

284
00:18:25,433 --> 00:18:26,833
Yeah, I'm not so sure
